sg":"太多感情線...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:19:14.000Z","msg":"唔恐怖？"},{"pid":"2a0c86f9cf116327a79354ff8e9ac0633b2fd7b4","tid":1748533,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cdab61048000fc9248a895a84bea1f48c393568","tid":1748533,"uid":160051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"977a5aa168d5d1b031896c9677fb61d069d45484","tid":1748533,"uid":209657,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"以下6間上映《返校》戲院：<br />\n<br />\n上環Soho House<br />\n銅鑼灣Cinema City Victoria <br />\n旺角Cinema City 朗豪坊<br />\n元朗戲院<br />\n新光戲院<br />\n葵涌Lumen Cinema"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T11:37:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>問：大家知唔知《返校》個發行商係邊撚個？</strong><br />\n答：係黃百嗚個女間公司，佢仲要陰陰濕濕唔出公司名，九成係驚人哋知係藍到黑公司就唔睇<br />\n<br />\n<strong>問：你知唔知上映電影嘅分紅點計？</strong><br />\n答：戲院（50%），發行商（25%），片主（25%）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>問：邊間戲院會上《返校》？</strong><br />\n答：Cinema City （黃百鳴開嘅戲院）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>問：去其它黃戲院睇囉？</strong><br />\n答：新光係神棍李居明嘅，其它有興趣自己FC一下背景<br />\n<br />\n<strong>問：睇返校會益邊個？</strong><br />\n答：首先益咗戲院（黃百鳴），之後益咗發行商（黃百鳴個女），最後先係台灣片主<br />\n<br />\n<strong>問：如果我想用金錢支持《返校》咁應該點做？</strong><br />\n答：等台灣出碟先買 / 去台灣時睇下戲院仲有冇得睇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TL；DR：喺香港睇《返校》就係益撚咗奶共黃百鳴</span></span>"},{"pid":"03416619d368ca8e0131a886a42f4c0e62e1ca2a","tid":1748533,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T11:40:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}